  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age 18-40 yr,

          -  metformin treatment for at least 3 months before entering the pregnancy,

          -  gestational age between 5 and 12 wk

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  diabetes mellitus

          -  significant liver or renal impairment

          -  neoplasms and other endocrine diseases

          -  the use of drugs other than metformin able to interfere with glucose and insulin
             metabolism.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
